|GKB-- Stump ----------------------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBTellurian|000
Command: |CKBstump|000
Guild Level: 10

Stump asks the earth for a quiet place to rest.  The druid waves a
hand, the ground rumbles, and a mossy stump grows up from below.
The druid settles onto it, breathes deeply, and small woodland friends
come out to keep watch.

While the druid remains seated on the stump, the Tellurian current
restores health in steady pulses based on Druid guild level.  The
stump is not a combat escape: standing, leaving, fighting, death, or
the end of the working sends the animals scampering away.

Use |CKBstand|000 or |CKBstand up|000 when you are ready to leave the
stump and wave goodbye to your friends.
